    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 guidance. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1 at all operating points with agreement within acceptance thresholds. The CFD model is deemed sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. A screening sensitivity study performed during model development confirmed low sensitivity of RH predictions to mesh density and blood viscosity parameter variations, providing additional confidence in the nominal simulation results.",
